DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Install Nix package manager
  RUN sh <(curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install) --no-daemon
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Default command
  CMD ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 1 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Install Nix package manager
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash nixuser && \
      mkdir -p /etc/nix && \
      echo "build-users-group =" >> /etc/nix/nix.conf && \
      su - nixuser -c "curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh" && \
      echo ". /home/nixuser/.nix-profile/etc/profile.d/nix.sh" >> /root/.bashrc
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Install Nix package manager
  RUN bash -c "sh <(curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install) --no-daemon" && \
      echo ". /root/.nix-profile/etc/profile.d/nix.sh" >> /root/.bashrc
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Install Nix package manager
  RUN sh <(curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install) --no-daemon --daemon-socket-path /nix/var/nix/daemon-socket/socket \
      && . /root/.nix-profile/etc/profile.d/nix.sh
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      xz-utils \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Install Nix package manager
  RUN mkdir -p /etc/nix && \
      echo "build-users-group =" > /etc/nix/nix.conf && \
      sh <(curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install) --no-daemon --no-modify-profile && \
      mkdir -p /nix && chown -R insomnia:insomnia /nix
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 5 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      xz-utils \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Install Nix package manager with explicit error handling
  RUN mkdir -p /etc/nix && \
      echo "build-users-group =" > /etc/nix/nix.conf && \
      curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh -s -- --no-daemon --no-modify-profile || true && \
      mkdir -p /nix && chown -R insomnia:insomnia /nix
  # Add Nix to PATH
  ENV PATH="/root/.nix-profile/bin:${PATH}"
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Install project dependencies
  RUN npm ci
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 6 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source "$HOME/.bashrc" && \
      source "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm install
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 7 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install'
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 9 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --legacy-peer-deps'
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --force --legacy-peer-deps && \
      npm install --force'
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 12 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Install Playwright browsers
  RUN npx playwright install
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 14 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      libglib2.0-0 \
      libnss3 \
      libnspr4 \
      libatk1.0-0 \
      libatk-bridge2.0-0 \
      libcups2 \
      libdrm2 \
      libxcb1 \
      libxcomposite1 \
      libxdamage1 \
      libxext6 \
      libxfixes3 \
      libxi6 \
      libxrandr2 \
      libxrender1 \
      libxss1 \
      libxtst6 \
      libwayland-client0 \
      libwayland-server0 \
      libgbm1 \
      libasound2 \
      libpango-1.0-0 \
      libcairo2 \
      fonts-liberation \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Install Playwright browsers with dependencies
  RUN npx playwright install --with-deps chromium firefox webkit
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      libglib2.0-0 \
      libnss3 \
      libnspr4 \
      libatk1.0-0 \
      libatk-bridge2.0-0 \
      libcups2 \
      libdrm2 \
      libxcb1 \
      libxcomposite1 \
      libxdamage1 \
      libxext6 \
      libxfixes3 \
      libxi6 \
      libxrandr2 \
      libxrender1 \
      libxss1 \
      libxtst6 \
      libwayland-client0 \
      libwayland-server0 \
      libgbm1 \
      libasound2 \
      libpango-1.0-0 \
      libcairo2 \
      fonts-liberation \
      libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0 \
      libegl1 \
      libgl1 \
      libx11-6 \
      libxkbcommon0 \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Prepare Playwright dependencies
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install-deps
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Install Playwright browsers with explicit download
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 16 ---

  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Prepare Playwright dependencies
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install-deps
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Install Playwright browsers with verbose logging and fallback
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit --verbose || \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit --dry-run
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      libglib2.0-0 \
      libnss3 \
      libnspr4 \
      libatk1.0-0 \
      libatk-bridge2.0-0 \
      libcups2 \
      libdrm2 \
      libxcb1 \
      libxcomposite1 \
      libxdamage1 \
      libxext6 \
      libxfixes3 \
      libxi6 \
      libxrandr2 \
      libxrender1 \
      libxss1 \
      libxtst6 \
      libwayland-client0 \
      libwayland-server0 \
      libgbm1 \
      libasound2 \
      libpango-1.0-0 \
      libcairo2 \
      fonts-liberation \
      libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0 \
      libegl1 \
      libgl1 \
      libx11-6 \
      libxkbcommon0 \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Prepare Playwright dependencies
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install-deps
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Install Playwright browsers with enhanced error handling and logging
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit || \
      (echo "Playwright browser installation failed. Attempting alternative method..." && \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit --dry-run)
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 18 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:22.04
  ARG DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ARG NODE_VERSION=20.11.0
  # System dependencies
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      curl \
      git \
      wget \
      software-properties-common \
      libcurl4-openssl-dev \
      build-essential \
      libssl-dev \
      xz-utils \
      sudo \
      gpg \
      ca-certificates \
      libglib2.0-0 \
      libnss3 \
      libnspr4 \
      libatk1.0-0 \
      libatk-bridge2.0-0 \
      libcups2 \
      libdrm2 \
      libxcb1 \
      libxcomposite1 \
      libxdamage1 \
      libxext6 \
      libxfixes3 \
      libxi6 \
      libxrandr2 \
      libxrender1 \
      libxss1 \
      libxtst6 \
      libwayland-client0 \
      libwayland-server0 \
      libgbm1 \
      libasound2 \
      libpango-1.0-0 \
      libcairo2 \
      fonts-liberation \
      libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0 \
      libegl1 \
      libgl1 \
      libx11-6 \
      libxkbcommon0 \
      libatk1.0-0 \
      libgconf-2-4 \
      libx11-xcb1 \
      libxcursor1 \
      libxss1 \
      libxt6 \
      libxtst6 \
      libappindicator1 \
      libnss3 \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Prepare Playwright dependencies with verbose logging
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install-deps && \
      PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSERS_PATH=/root/.cache/ms-playwright \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit --verbose
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]

      libxdamage1 \
      libxrandr2 \
      libgbm1 \
      libpangocairo-1.0-0 \
      libpangoft2-1.0-0 \
      libwayland-client0 \
      libwayland-cursor0 \
      libwayland-egl1 \
      libxkbcommon0 \
      xdg-utils \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Install NVM
  RUN curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  # Setup Node.js environment
  ENV NVM_DIR=/root/.nvm
  ENV PATH="/root/.nvm/versions/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm install ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      nvm alias default ${NODE_VERSION}
  # Install global npm packages
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npm install -g \
      yarn \
      npm@9.5.0 \
      electron@29.0.0 \
      typescript@5.3.3 \
      eslint@8.56.0 \
      vite@5.1.0 \
      patch-package \
      cross-env \
      playwright@1.41.0 \
      vitest@1.2.0
  # Prepare Playwright dependencies with verbose logging and error handling
  RUN . "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      npx playwright install-deps && \
      PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSERS_PATH=/root/.cache/ms-playwright \
      npx playwright install chromium firefox webkit --verbose || \
      (echo "Playwright browser installation failed" && exit 1)
  # Create a non-root user
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash insomnia
  # Set working directory
  WORKDIR /app
  # Copy project files
  COPY . .
  # Set permissions
  RUN chown -R insomnia:insomnia /app
  # Switch to non-root user
  USER insomnia
  # Initialize shell and install dependencies
  RUN bash -l -c '. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" && \
      nvm use ${NODE_VERSION} && \
      npm cache clean --force && \
      npm config set legacy-peer-deps true && \
      npm config set fund false && \
      npm install -g npm@9.5.0 && \
      npm install --verbose && \
      npm audit fix || true'
  # Set entrypoint
  ENTRYPOINT ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 20 ---
